# Copy this file to .env.local.
#
# STRONGLY RECOMMENDED: set a custom devnet RPC URL below.
# The default public endpoint (https://api.devnet.solana.com) is heavily
# rate-limited and frequently BLOCKS browser reads (403 / 429). The usual symptom
# is that SOL and token balances show up blank in the web app. A free RPC from
# Helius / QuickNode / Alchemy fixes this instantly.
#
# Get a free devnet RPC URL (any one of these):
#   - Helius:    https://dashboard.helius.dev  -> copy the devnet URL
#   - QuickNode: https://www.quicknode.com     -> create a Solana devnet endpoint
#   - Alchemy:   https://dashboard.alchemy.com -> Solana devnet app
#
# Then paste it here (example shape shown):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_URL=https://devnet.helius-rpc.com/?api-key=YOUR_KEY
NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_URL=

# After editing this file, restart the dev server:  npm run dev
